+ Chain Transformations\nfor Readable Pipelines
++ Lazy Evaluation
+++ Operations not executed immediately
++++_ Execute on action (display/show)
+++ Spark optimizes entire sequence
++++_ Query plan optimization
++ Method Chaining
+++ filter() → groupBy() → agg() → sort()
++++_ Each step builds on previous
++++_ Parentheses for multi-line
-- Best Practices
---_ Place filters first
---_ Reduces data for subsequent steps
---_ Improves readability
---_ Clear data flow from source to result
